##17 April 1999
Jason called this morning. He was all, &ldquo;Rob, wanna go to Australia with me for four months?&rdquo;
whoah! said my brain. &ldquo;Whoah. Four months?&rdquo;
&ldquo;Yeah. My mom said that I should travel before I try to do anything else so I told her &lsquo;okay; me and Rob are going to Australia.&rsquo;&rdquo;
&ldquo;Wow. That would be totally great, and I can see the value in it.
